<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Footnotes">Footnotes</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Copts&amp;action=edit&amp;section=24" title="Edit section: Footnotes">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
