</li>
<li id="cite_note-155"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-155">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1133582631"><cite id="CITEREFTahaElzalabanyFawziHisham2020" class="citation journal cs1">Taha, Tarek; Elzalabany, Sagy; Fawzi, Sahar; Hisham, Ahmed; Amer, Khaled; Shaker, Olfat (August 2020). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/32521421/">"Allele frequency comparative study between the two main Egyptian ethnic groups"</a>. <i>Forensic Science International</i>. <b>313</b>: 110348. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.1016%2Fj.forsciint.2020.110348">10.1016/j.forsciint.2020.110348</a>. <a href="/wiki/ISSN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISSN (identifier)">ISSN</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.worldcat.org/issn/1872-6283">1872-6283</a>. <a href="/wiki/PMID_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="PMID (identifier)">PMID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/32521421">32521421</a>. <a href="/wiki/S2CID_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="S2CID (identifier)">S2CID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://api.semanticscholar.org/CorpusID:219586129">219586129</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Forensic+Science+International&amp;rft.atitle=Allele+frequency+comparative+study+between+the+two+main+Egyptian+ethnic+groups&amp;rft.volume=313&amp;rft.pages=110348&amp;rft.date=2020-08&amp;rft.issn=1872-6283&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.semanticscholar.org%2FCorpusID%3A219586129%23id-name%3DS2CID&amp;rft_id=info%3Apmid%2F32521421&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1016%2Fj.forsciint.2020.110348&amp;rft.aulast=Taha&amp;rft.aufi